$Id$

This directory, ~/sltsbl, contains routines to generate and parameterize 
saltation-sandblasting physics simulations. The original routines are all 
by Alf Grini who implemented the saltation-sandblasting theory of Alfaro 
& Gomes (2001).

lookuptable_final.f	Alf's original (F77) code, unmodified
sltsbl.F90		Cleaned up, F95 version of Alf's code
formatlab.m		MATLAB routines for plotting data
